divs: Sighting Details I walked outside to smoke a cig and looked upbecause I just heard about the Phonicx lights and I saw this red light go flyingover I know it was not a aircraft it had no blinking lights it was going to fastto be a normal plane and it was very low it made no sound at all it just flewout of sight I yelled at my friends in the house but it was to late it was gone
